text: Situated at a beautiful park (Labrador Park). It is accessible by car or public transport (you can walk from Labrador Park/ Harbour Front MRT station, est 1km). My usual starting point is from Harbour Front centre, to Keppel bay and all the way to Labrador Park. Best spot to enjoy sunset, sea breeze and natures all together ðŸ¤©
A great place to enjoy sea breeze and relax.

You can get a great view of sunset from here.  Nice and clean place. People are making barbecue also. Full party mode . You have to bring everything with you to make barbecue. Car parking is also available.
A nice and less crowded place which you can enjoy peacefulness or cool down. If you are lucky, you will be able to spot some roosters around. Enjoy and have fun!
Very quiet and peaceful park. Not too crowded and quite deep in and fun to explore. Can see beautiful singapore landscapes too
